# Technical Design Document
## EDP Order Entity — Canonical Event Schema
**Project:** gamma · **Phase:** Design Event Schema
**Author:** Lead Architect · **Status:** PROPOSED
**Constraints verified:** gamma-c1 through gamma-c7 · **Safety check:** ✅ PASS

