## ⚠️ Operational Note on Decision Persistence

The `save_decision` tool returned HTTP 422 (`sessionId required`) on all attempts — no session ID was issued at session start. **All decisions in this document must be manually committed to the ADR register** until the session-management issue is resolved. This is flagged as Open Question #OQ-8 below.

